<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Virtual Counselling | The Admission Architect</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <style> body { padding-top: 0 !important; } </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

    <header class="landing-hero" style="height: 60vh; background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(230, 81, 0, 0.9), rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.7)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497019940-1c28c88b4f3e?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1920&q=80') center/cover;">
        <h1 style="font-size: 50px;">Virtual Counselling</h1>
        <p>Expert 1-on-1 guidance from anywhere in the world.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="container" style="max-width: 900px; padding: 60px 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Your Dedicated Expert Advisor</h2>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            Distance is no longer a barrier to securing world-class education consultancy. Through our Virtual Counselling sessions, you get uninterrupted, dedicated time with our senior admission strategists via Google Meet or Zoom. 
        </p>

        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            During these sessions, we will map out your academic timeline, review your personal statement drafts, address visa concerns, and help you select the exact test preparation modules you need.
        </p>

        <div style="text-align: center; background: #FFF3E0; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; border: 2px solid #FF9800;">
            <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: #E65100;">Let's talk about your future.</h2>
            <p style="color: #555; margin-bottom: 25px;">Book a time that works perfectly for your time zone directly through our portal.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="calc-btn-primary" style="background: #E65100; display: inline-block; width: auto; padding: 15px 40px;">Sign in & Book a Session</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>